<title type="html"><![CDATA[11/17(THU.)Aggressive hard sell &amp;The FIFA World Cup 2022™ in Qatar (Host:shuman)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=670&amp;p=698#p698"><![CDATA[
11/17(THU.)Aggressive hard sell &amp;The FIFA World Cup 2022™ in Qatar (Host:shuman) <br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br /><br />HOW TO AVOID THE AGGRESSIVE HARD SELL<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.thecpa.co.uk/news/genuine-tradespeople/">https://www.thecpa.co.uk/news/genuine-tradespeople/</a><!-- m --><br />Question<br />1.Aggressive hard sell may happen everywhere. Have you ever met aggressive hard sell? Share your story.<br />2.If hard sell person were your friends or relatives how to deal with? Can you share some good excuses for us?<br />3.Do you feel guilty if you didn’t support them?<br />4.What is an ideal salesman?<br />5.     Free to ask.<br />-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />The FIFA World Cup 2022™ in Qatar<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://publications.fifa.com/en/sustainability-report/sustainability-at-the-fifa-world-cup/profile-of-the-fifa-world-cup-qatar-2022/">https://publications.fifa.com/en/sustai ... atar-2022/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.Have you ever watched the FIFA World Cup before? Do you have favor team?<br />2.Have you ever supported any kind of professional sport teams?<br />3.Does any player make you admire?<br />4.Which one do you prefer, watch on TV or go to stadium? Why?<br />5. Free to ask.<br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Thu Nov 10, 2022 9:09 pm</p><hr />
